{"tid":2110522,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"[何文田加多利峯] 持貨5年蝕逾600萬","createTime":"2020-07-16T03:38:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T09:03:40.000Z","uid":73269,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"bf8276250f7c61de4037c03924e9cd7079e5ce0d","tid":2110522,"uid":73269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:38:57.000Z","msg":"豪宅<br />\n<br />\n市場再錄得內地客沽貨，由內地人士持有的何文田加多利峯單位，剛以1,950萬元沽出，連同雜項費用計算，實蝕逾600萬元。<br />\n土地註冊處顯示，加多利峯中層B室，登記以1,950萬元售出，實用面積959平方呎，呎價20,334元。原業主為內地人士，於2015年以2,057萬元購入單位，單計帳面已蝕107萬元，若連同當年須額外繳23.5%的辣招稅計算，則<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>實蝕逾600萬元</strong></span></span>。"},{"pid":"3a185369fac99ef5d047a5db910fa88036b1444a","tid":2110522,"uid":353629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:43:55.000Z","msg":"走資姐"},{"pid":"f63cf2a54b42fe18152003e74d8c6a57262f9b64","tid":2110522,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"仲係過2萬一呎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bd98d0484a524020db5c649af12f50de719fb50","tid":2110522,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f63cf2a54b42fe18152003e74d8c6a57262f9b64","tid":2110522,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"仲係過2萬一呎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T04:04:47.000Z","msg":"市區豪宅2萬元一呎算平喇<br />\n太古城都要啦"},{"pid":"2a82cc4e886d96de2f1b497abe1cd34ab55c147a","tid":2110522,"uid":127044,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2bd98d0484a524020db5c649af12f50de719fb50","tid":2110522,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f63cf2a54b42fe18152003e74d8c6a57262f9b64","tid":2110522,"uid":75994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T03:48:09.000Z","msg":"仲係過2萬一呎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"r